# Alpaca Paper Trading API Keys
# Required for both Netlify functions and local dev proxy
#
# Get your keys from: https://app.alpaca.markets/paper/dashboard/overview → API Keys tab
# If you don't see your secret key, click "Generate New Key" to create a new key pair
#
# CRITICAL: Set ALPACA_SECRET_KEY in Netlify Dashboard → Site Settings → Environment Variables
# The proxy function will return 401 errors without this key set.
#
ALPACA_API_KEY=PKFJY5TRMF36BGN76LPRGRUKTO
ALPACA_SECRET_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_ALPACA_SECRET_KEY